0 LANCER~
&w
LANCER

This is a class of warrior much in the same vein as Chevaliers, who uphold
a high personal code of honor and travel the world to protect those in 
need. They are of the races which cannot ride mounts, and thus are unable 
to develop the same sort of fighting style as that used by a Chevalier. 
Some take advantage of their ability to BE mounted to mimic the style used 
by their counterparts, while othersneither able to ride a mount to battle 
nor to provide service as onehave developed a style that heavily employs 
their speed and strength in combination with spears and similar weapons to 
strike enemies from further away, harder.

One who is unmountable and does not possess hooves is not capable of 
becoming a Lancer due to the physical requirements of this style of life, 
but might be better suited to being a Chevalier. 

~

